<plot>Grandma Goth, a documentary short, "digs up" the obsessive death-related collection of 64-year-old Suelynn Gustafson, who calls herself Grandma Goth. This magenta-haired maven of the dark side, takes us on a tour of her coffin filled historic church and her Halloween costume shop--spouting her morbid musings along the way.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?221753</url></doc>
